Interface PyObjectAdapter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClassAdapter, ClassicPyObjectAdapter, ExtensiblePyObjectAdapter

    public interface PyObjectAdapter
    PyObjectAdapters turn Java Objects into PyObjects.
